name: R5-Claim-R4B-Claim
title: Concept map to convert a FHIR R5 Claim into FHIR R4B

target.comment: R5 `Claim` maps as Equivalent to R4B `Claim`
R5 `Claim.accident` maps as Equivalent to R4B `Claim.accident`
R5 `Claim.accident.date` maps as Equivalent to R4B `Claim.accident.date`

R5 `Claim.accident.extension` maps as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget to R4B `Claim.accident.extension` - extension has change due to type change: R5 `extension` `Extension` maps as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget for R4B `extension`
R5 `Claim.accident.id` maps as Equivalent to R4B `Claim.accident.id`
R5 `Claim.accident.location[x]` maps as Equivalent to R4B `Claim.accident.location[x]`
